com.meterware.httpunit
Interface HTMLElement

All Superinterfaces:
ScriptingEventHandler
All Known Implementing Classes:
BlockElement, com.meterware.httpunit.HTMLElementBase, WebRequestSource
public interface HTMLElement
extends ScriptingEventHandler

An interface which defines the common properties for an HTML element, which can correspond to any HTML tag.

Since:
1.5.2
Author:
Russell Gold
